beer.beer_description:
Jump on board the Last Tram to Brunswick, spiritual successor to our popular & first - ever NEIPA, Last Train To Boston. 
Fully loaded with a hefty dose of LUPOMAX El Dorado and Galaxy in the whirlpool. Double dry hopped with LUPOMAX El Dorado, LUPOMAX Amarillo, and Galaxy creating huge tropical pineapple and apricot aromas that leap from the glass.
Don’t forget to tap on.
Whirlpool hop: 4.5g/l
Dry hop: 15g/l
